    <title>如何把Matplotlib嵌入到PyQt中？</title>
    <url>/archives/b45b/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="简介">简介</h1>
<p>最近在学习PyQt，想到之前对Matplotlib用得还挺熟的，便想着能否把Matplotlib的内容嵌入到PyQt中。其实方法还挺简单的，在这里分享一个例子给大家。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h1 id="一个类">一个类</h1>
<p>首先需要import一个类——<code>FigureCanvasQTAgg</code>，它是沟通Matplotlib和PyQt的桥梁，它既是Matplotlib的类，也是PyQt的类：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> matplotlib.backends.backend_qt5agg <span class="keyword">import</span> FigureCanvasQTAgg <span class="keyword">as</span> FigureCanvas</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="用matplotlib绘图">用Matplotlib绘图</h1>
<p>这里画的是 <span class="math inline"><mjx-container class="MathJax" jax="SVG"><svg style="vertical-align: -0.566ex" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="9.713ex" height="2.262ex" role="img" focusable="false" viewBox="0 -750 4293 1000"><g stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" transform="scale(1,-1)"><g data-mml-node="math"><g data-mml-node="mi"><path data-c="1D453" d="M118 -162Q120 -162 124 -164T135 -167T147 -168Q160 -168 171 -155T187 -126Q197 -99 221 27T267 267T289 382V385H242Q195 385 192 387Q188 390 188 397L195 425Q197 430 203 430T250 431Q298 431 298 432Q298 434 307 482T319 540Q356 705 465 705Q502 703 526 683T550 630Q550 594 529 578T487 561Q443 561 443 603Q443 622 454 636T478 657L487 662Q471 668 457 668Q445 668 434 658T419 630Q412 601 403 552T387 469T380 433Q380 431 435 431Q480 431 487 430T498 424Q499 420 496 407T491 391Q489 386 482 386T428 385H372L349 263Q301 15 282 -47Q255 -132 212 -173Q175 -205 139 -205Q107 -205 81 -186T55 -132Q55 -95 76 -78T118 -61Q162 -61 162 -103Q162 -122 151 -136T127 -157L118 -162Z"></path></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(550,0)"><path data-c="28" d="M94 250Q94 319 104 381T127 488T164 576T202 643T244 695T277 729T302 750H315H319Q333 750 333 741Q333 738 316 720T275 667T226 581T184 443T167 250T184 58T225 -81T274 -167T316 -220T333 -241Q333 -250 318 -250H315H302L274 -226Q180 -141 137 -14T94 250Z"></path></g><g data-mml-node="mi" transform="translate(939,0)"><path data-c="1D465" d="M52 289Q59 331 106 386T222 442Q257 442 286 424T329 379Q371 442 430 442Q467 442 494 420T522 361Q522 332 508 314T481 292T458 288Q439 288 427 299T415 328Q415 374 465 391Q454 404 425 404Q412 404 406 402Q368 386 350 336Q290 115 290 78Q290 50 306 38T341 26Q378 26 414 59T463 140Q466 150 469 151T485 153H489Q504 153 504 145Q504 144 502 134Q486 77 440 33T333 -11Q263 -11 227 52Q186 -10 133 -10H127Q78 -10 57 16T35 71Q35 103 54 123T99 143Q142 143 142 101Q142 81 130 66T107 46T94 41L91 40Q91 39 97 36T113 29T132 26Q168 26 194 71Q203 87 217 139T245 247T261 313Q266 340 266 352Q266 380 251 392T217 404Q177 404 142 372T93 290Q91 281 88 280T72 278H58Q52 284 52 289Z"></path></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(1511,0)"><path data-c="29" d="M60 749L64 750Q69 750 74 750H86L114 726Q208 641 251 514T294 250Q294 182 284 119T261 12T224 -76T186 -143T145 -194T113 -227T90 -246Q87 -249 86 -250H74Q66 -250 63 -250T58 -247T55 -238Q56 -237 66 -225Q221 -64 221 250T66 725Q56 737 55 738Q55 746 60 749Z"></path></g><g data-mml-node="mo" transform="translate(2177.8,0)"><path data-c="3D" d="M56 347Q56 360 70 367H707Q722 359 722 347Q722 336 708 328L390 327H72Q56 332 56 347ZM56 153Q56 168 72 173H708Q722 163 722 153Q722 140 707 133H70Q56 140 56 153Z"></path></g><g data-mml-node="msup" transform="translate(3233.6,0)"><g data-mml-node="mi"><path data-c="1D465" d="M52 289Q59 331 106 386T222 442Q257 442 286 424T329 379Q371 442 430 442Q467 442 494 420T522 361Q522 332 508 314T481 292T458 288Q439 288 427 299T415 328Q415 374 465 391Q454 404 425 404Q412 404 406 402Q368 386 350 336Q290 115 290 78Q290 50 306 38T341 26Q378 26 414 59T463 140Q466 150 469 151T485 153H489Q504 153 504 145Q504 144 502 134Q486 77 440 33T333 -11Q263 -11 227 52Q186 -10 133 -10H127Q78 -10 57 16T35 71Q35 103 54 123T99 143Q142 143 142 101Q142 81 130 66T107 46T94 41L91 40Q91 39 97 36T113 29T132 26Q168 26 194 71Q203 87 217 139T245 247T261 313Q266 340 266 352Q266 380 251 392T217 404Q177 404 142 372T93 290Q91 281 88 280T72 278H58Q52 284 52 289Z"></path></g><g data-mml-node="mi" transform="translate(605,363) scale(0.707)"><path data-c="1D465" d="M52 289Q59 331 106 386T222 442Q257 442 286 424T329 379Q371 442 430 442Q467 442 494 420T522 361Q522 332 508 314T481 292T458 288Q439 288 427 299T415 328Q415 374 465 391Q454 404 425 404Q412 404 406 402Q368 386 350 336Q290 115 290 78Q290 50 306 38T341 26Q378 26 414 59T463 140Q466 150 469 151T485 153H489Q504 153 504 145Q504 144 502 134Q486 77 440 33T333 -11Q263 -11 227 52Q186 -10 133 -10H127Q78 -10 57 16T35 71Q35 103 54 123T99 143Q142 143 142 101Q142 81 130 66T107 46T94 41L91 40Q91 39 97 36T113 29T132 26Q168 26 194 71Q203 87 217 139T245 247T261 313Q266 340 266 352Q266 380 251 392T217 404Q177 404 142 372T93 290Q91 281 88 280T72 278H58Q52 284 52 289Z"></path></g></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container></span> 的图像。</p>
<p>想要绘图的话，先新建一个类，并继承<code>FigureCanvasQTAgg</code>：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> matplotlib.figure <span class="keyword">import</span> Figure</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Draw</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">FigureCanvas</span>):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, dpi=<span class="number">128</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.fig = Figure(dpi=dpi) <span class="comment"># 新建一个 Figure 对象，用于绘图</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">super</span>().__init__(self.fig)</span><br><span class="line">        self.axes = self.fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        self.draw_function()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">draw_function</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 实际的绘图函数</span></span><br><span class="line">        x = np.arange(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0.01</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        y = x ** x</span><br><span class="line">        self.axes.plot(x, y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="设置pyqt窗口">设置PyQt窗口</h1>
<p>要布局的话，用Qt Designer是很不错的，这里是ui文件，作个参考：</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ui</span> <span class="attr">version</span>=<span class="string">"4.0"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">class</span>&gt;</span>draw<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">class</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">widget</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"QDialog"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"draw"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"geometry"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">rect</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span>480<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span>320<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">rect</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"minimumSize"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"maximumSize"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span>16777215<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span>16777215<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"windowTitle"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span> <span class="attr">notr</span>=<span class="string">"true"</span>&gt;</span>matplotlib with pyqt<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">layout</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"QVBoxLayout"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"verticalLayout"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"leftMargin"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span>9<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"topMargin"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span>9<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"rightMargin"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span>9<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"bottomMargin"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span>9<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">number</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">item</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">widget</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"QLabel"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"label"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"minimumSize"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span>0<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span>32<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"maximumSize"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span>16777215<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">width</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span>32<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">height</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">size</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span>f(x)=x^x的图像:<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">string</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">widget</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">item</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">item</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">widget</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"QDialogButtonBox"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"buttonBox"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"standardButtons"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">set</span>&gt;</span>QDialogButtonBox::Cancel|QDialogButtonBox::Ok<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">set</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">widget</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">item</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">layout</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">widget</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">resources</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">connections</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">connection</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sender</span>&gt;</span>buttonBox<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sender</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">signal</span>&gt;</span>accepted()<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">signal</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">receiver</span>&gt;</span>draw<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">receiver</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">slot</span>&gt;</span>accept()<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">slot</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hints</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hint</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"sourcelabel"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span>343<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span>297<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hint</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hint</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"destinationlabel"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span>334<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span>320<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hint</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hints</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">connection</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">connection</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sender</span>&gt;</span>buttonBox<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sender</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">signal</span>&gt;</span>rejected()<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">signal</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">receiver</span>&gt;</span>draw<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">receiver</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">slot</span>&gt;</span>reject()<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">slot</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hints</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hint</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"sourcelabel"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span>434<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span>300<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hint</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hint</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"destinationlabel"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span>444<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">x</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span>313<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">y</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hint</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">hints</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">connection</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">connections</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ui</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>把ui文件编译为py文件之后，就可以在程序中使用了：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> sys</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> PyQt5.QtWidgets <span class="keyword">import</span> QApplication, QDialog</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> Ui_ui <span class="keyword">import</span> Ui_draw</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">DrawDialog</span>(QDialog, Ui_draw):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">super</span>().__init__()</span><br><span class="line">        self.setupUi(self)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        self.drawWidget = Draw()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 原本有两个部件，上面是一个 QLabel，下面是一个 QButtonBox</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 在垂直布局中插入绘图部件</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.verticalLayout.insertWidget(<span class="number">1</span>, self.drawWidget)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        self.show()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">main</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    app = QApplication(sys.argv)</span><br><span class="line">    form = DrawDialog()</span><br><span class="line">    sys.exit(app.exec_())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="总的程序">总的程序</h1>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> sys</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> matplotlib.backends.backend_qt5agg <span class="keyword">import</span> FigureCanvasQTAgg <span class="keyword">as</span> FigureCanvas</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> matplotlib.figure <span class="keyword">import</span> Figure</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> PyQt5.QtWidgets <span class="keyword">import</span> QApplication, QDialog</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> Ui_ui <span class="keyword">import</span> Ui_draw</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Draw</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">FigureCanvas</span>):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, dpi=<span class="number">128</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.fig = Figure(dpi=dpi) <span class="comment"># 新建一个 Figure 对象，用于绘图</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">super</span>().__init__(self.fig)</span><br><span class="line">        self.axes = self.fig.add_subplot(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        self.draw_function()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">draw_function</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 实际的绘图函数</span></span><br><span class="line">        x = np.arange(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0.01</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        y = x ** x</span><br><span class="line">        self.axes.plot(x, y)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">DrawDialog</span>(QDialog, Ui_draw):</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">super</span>().__init__()</span><br><span class="line">        self.setupUi(self)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        self.drawWidget = Draw()</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 原本有两个部件，上面是一个 QLabel，下面是一个 QButtonBox</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 在垂直布局中插入绘图部件</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.verticalLayout.insertWidget(<span class="number">1</span>, self.drawWidget)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        self.show()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">main</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    app = QApplication(sys.argv)</span><br><span class="line">    form = DrawDialog()</span><br><span class="line">    sys.exit(app.exec_())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
